== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1984 i Soweto, muri [[Afurika y'Epfo]] mu muryango wa politiki. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-10-19-isidingos-motlatsi-on-being-judged-for-coming-from-ekasi-it-doesnt-make-me-uneducated/</ref>

Yashakanye na Millicent Nkangane, umunyamideli kuva mu Gushyingo 2014. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2017-10-04-motlatsi-mafatshes-wife-thank-you-for-making-sure-im-the-best/</ref> Bahuriye bwa mbere mu rusengero. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2019-02-14-v-day--heres-how-isidingos-motlatsi--his-wifey-keep-the-flame-alive/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yakinnye 'Sechaba' ku isabune izwi cyane ya SABC 3 ''Isidingo'' muri 2010. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2020-01-17-motlatsi-mafatshe-says-actors-found-out-about-isidingo-chop-on-twitter/</ref> Amaze gukina imyaka irenga icyenda, yaje kwinjira kumugaragaro mu itsinda ryayobora iki gitaramo muri 2018. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-10-15-motlatsi-mafatshe-on-becoming-a-isidingo-director-im-more-than-just-sechaba/</ref> <ref>https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/entertainment/2020-04-11-what-motlatsi-mafatshes-doing-after-isidingo-he-wont-give-up-on-directing-dream/</ref> Muri 2019, yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu bakinnyi ba mbere muri Royalty Soapie Awards. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/isidingos-motlatsi-mafatshe-on-playing-sechaba-moloi-for-over-9-years-20190430</ref>

Yakinnye kandi nka 'Wandile Dhlomo' mu ikinamico y'umupira w'amaguru ''Shooting Stars'' . Hanyuma yagaragaye afite uruhare 'Casper' murukurikirane ''Iyo Twari Umwirabura'' .  Muri 2018, yafatanije gukora romcom ''Love Lives Here'' . <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/motlatsi-mafatshe-the-actor-turned-producer-20180308</ref>

Ku ya 3 Gashyantare 2006, yibasiwe n'umuhanzi wa hip hop Thulani Ngcobo uzwi ku izina rya 'Pitch Black Afro' mu birori bya mbere bya Afurika y'Epfo kuri televiziyo ya ''Tsotsi'' .

